---
Author : hdela


---
This mod was built with Skyrim US Ver 1.5.24.0


---
Installation : Unzip the file, and overwrite Skyrim Data folder. Or drop the esp into your Skyrim Data directory.


---
Ver 1.1

You can go to \"Another Solitude\" by operating the Time Macine.

NOTICE : This time machine cannot be operated if you have sat on a chair.


Ver 1.0 : First MOD

Double bed x1
No respawn container x6

Alchemy Workbench
Enchanting Workbench
Shrine of Talos

Smelter Marker
BlackSmith Forge
Armor Workbench 
Blacksmith Sharpening Wheel
Tanning Rack Marker
Cooking Pot

---
Enjoy!

by hdela
